{"tid":2221393,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"喜歡你　鄭錦滿　任由途人發現","createTime":"2020-09-28T10:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T16:43:33.000Z","uid":343520,"like":25,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ee45f854efd9e6a98573089c123e3e96e41646b6","tid":2221393,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿（原曲：劉德華 - 17歲）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十幾歲那日不要臉　反興建高鐵<br />\n鄭錦滿去了讀書　短短幾年太新鮮<br />\n黃洋達哥　（大亨）　早已見過面　<br />\n後來...榮升主角太突然<br />\n<br />\n廿九歲當天想透了　港島裡挑戰<br />\n大亨泰博共云根一起　組成五區選<br />\n然後落街　派單    拉票太熟練　<br />\n然而成績只有心酸<br />\n<br />\n喜歡你　鄭錦滿　任由途人發現<br />\n我堅信　用心可永續那基本法<br />\n<br />\n熱民歌　齊齊來一遍　<br />\n無時無刻都記住本土需要錢<br />\n來選議會　又從頭再一遍　<br />\n<br />\n明年被取消資格難避免<br />\n勝率起跌　選區改變 <br />\n這首歌　為你拉票"},{"pid":"f8612b618d434acde335cced38b125f2327aff6c","tid":2221393,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b55c5c1ba268aeddcc37dc679f05e9ae9487ce4","tid":2221393,"uid":343520,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"喜歡的朋友可以幫手推推嘛？<br />\n黃色填詞人撐得好辛苦🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"705f7377da4ffa28660a74dce925d44a5f3bc41c","tid":2221393,"uid":60404,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:30:31.000Z","msg":"邊間教會？"},{"pid":"216f0d0f6e295674eb3c1ba7927babaf83e44b67","tid":2221393,"uid":266718,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"D人成日傳佢玩社運食好多女<br />\n有無人爆下料呢"},{"pid":"6816b1cbd6f61ebfaa616030ca3846931614012f","tid":2221393,"uid":163529,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"嚴重教會撚"},{"pid":"a2c121cffb67fb23953c232a664c212eee766724","tid":2221393,"uid":66514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:33:00.000Z","msg":"漏撚咗<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.l